<para>If HW spinlock id is invalid. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>-EBUSY</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>If HW spinlock is already locked by someone else. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
