        <briefdescription>
<para>Structure initializer for struct <ref refid="structhwspinlock__dt__spec" kindref="compound">hwspinlock_dt_spec</ref> from devicetree by index. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This helper macro expands to a static initializer for a struct <ref refid="structhwspinlock__dt__spec" kindref="compound">hwspinlock_dt_spec</ref> by reading the relevant device controller and id number from the devicetree.</para>
